gmoji\" /> 如果失敗左咁點搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:5月中就係一週年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽過男仔表示：女仔整手作都係滿足自己整一大輪野送比對方既心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自己拎到既滿足感分分鐘比男仔多出N倍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 皮革銀包你可以上ig search 好多開班教 不過就貴少少啦 我之前整過passport套 要成700幾左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd59425263ef8d87ed68d9d5115ab581b3fdbae","tid":200424,"uid":93493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>送過手織頸巾兩條 立體卡 親手畫既畫 皮革銀包 相簿 一週年紀念仲送過一齊冇耐我自己偷偷地寫比佢既日記 仲有好多好多<br />\n結果係除左個銀包佢有用之外 所有野我都冇再出現過係我眼前 甚至擺係間房做擺設裝飾乜都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶翻個頭盔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非專業人士 但整啲野一定出得街見得下人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你整左咁多樣唔同既手作野都知 應該ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗我如果第一次麻麻地甚至失敗既 想再叫我有第二次都真係難啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca40cb526a6a1e6f9dbb6ecfa7aa320e84c3c3e","tid":200424,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>送過手織頸巾兩條 立體卡 親手畫既畫 皮革銀包 相簿 一週年紀念仲送過一齊冇耐我自己偷偷地寫比佢既日記 仲有好多好多<br />\n結果係除左個銀包佢有用之外 所有野我都冇再出現過係我眼前 甚至擺係間房做擺設裝飾乜都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif